This project use Prisma ORM 

https://www.prisma.io/docs/getting-started/setup-prisma/add-to-existing-project/relational-databases-node-mysql
for create a schema use this link : 
https://www.prisma.io/docs/reference/api-reference/prisma-schema-reference#string

for update schemas DB use this : npx prisma migrate dev --name xxxx
for fix a schema use this command line : prisma format
for access into function to prisma use : req.context.prisma 